--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 0.2.2 (2020-05-27)
B: Remove 'creates' Ansible parameter (make unarchive override files)

* Version 0.2.1 (2020-04-23)
B: Fix Jinja2 for-loop statement

* Version 0.2.0 (2020-04-23)
F: Add option to specify hosts (smokeping_prober_hosts)
B: Ensure 'cap_net_raw' capability is set
B: Correct default service parameters

* Version 0.1.0 (2020-04-23)
F: Initial release
